{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, according to their research, DL outperformed \"conventional\" ML baselines in 67% of the studies examined.",
    "A systematic literature review by Namoun and Alshanqiti (2021) investigated the prediction of student outcomes using ML models and data mining.",
    "This review focused on three areas: how learning outcomes can be predicted, predictive analytics models used for predicting student learning, and key variables influencing student performance.",
    "Achievement grades and performance class standards were used to gauge how well students had learned their objectives.",
    "The review mentioned that the most apparent indicators of learning outcomes were student academic mood, term assessment grades, and student online learning activities."
  ]
}